These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, ship, motorbike, airplane
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person driving the airplane##6
 5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 8. the person driving the ship is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the person driving the taxi is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
13. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Transport    | taxi         | airplane     | motorbike     | ship         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

