.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, jet-ski, car
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person driving the car is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | jet-ski          | skateboard      | car      | boat   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| Sport      | weightlifting | baseball    | badminton  | ice-hockey |

