House: modern, farmhouse, futuristic, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the modern house##1
 3. the modern house is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the palace house##1
 6. the palace house is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the futuristic house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the futuristic house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking       | card-games | gardening  | reading    |
| House   | futuristic       | palace    | farmhouse | modern    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | baseball   | lacrosse   | basketball |

