 7. the person driving the train is not the polish##6
 8. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the polish##8
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the polish##8
12. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
